graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web Console]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 20.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    Dashboard -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+<br/>REQUIRED]
    Dashboard -->|auth proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>REQUIRED]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| PatternFly[PatternFly 6.3.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    Dashboard -->|frontend| React[React 18.2.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    Dashboard -->|backend| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient["@kubernetes/client-node 0.12.2<br/>REQUIRED"]
    Dashboard -->|code editor| Monaco[Monaco Editor 0.50.0<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    Dashboard -.->|preferred platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Core
    Dashboard -->|monitors CRDs| ODHOperator[odh-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster/DSCInitialization]
    Dashboard -->|manages notebooks| NotebookController[notebook-controller<br/>Notebook CRD]
    Dashboard -->|manages registries| ModelRegistryOp[model-registry-operator<br/>ModelRegistry CRD]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Monitoring
    Dashboard -->|monitors| KServeController[kserve-controller<br/>InferenceService CRD]
    Dashboard -->|monitors| DistributedWorkloads[distributed-workloads<br/>Training Jobs]
    Dashboard -->|monitors| FeastOperator[feast-operator<br/>FeatureStore CRD]
    Dashboard -->|monitors| LlamaStackOp[llama-stack-operator<br/>LlamaStackDistribution CRD]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - APIs
    Dashboard -->|API proxy| KubeflowPipelines[kubeflow-pipelines<br/>Pipeline API]
    Dashboard -->|metrics| ThanosQuerier[thanos-querier<br/>Prometheus Metrics]
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OpenShiftOAuth[openshift-oauth<br/>OAuth2 Provider]

    %% Integration Points - User Interactions
    DataScientist[Data Scientist] -->|creates projects| Dashboard
    DataScientist -->|launches notebooks| Dashboard
    DataScientist -->|deploys models| Dashboard

    Admin[Administrator] -->|configures platform| Dashboard
    Admin -->|manages users| Dashboard

    %% Integration Points - Dashboard Initiates
    Dashboard -->|creates| NotebookPods[Jupyter Notebook Pods]
    Dashboard -->|creates| ModelRegistries[Model Registry Instances]
    Dashboard -->|monitors| InferenceServices[KServe InferenceServices]
    Dashboard -->|monitors| PipelineRuns[Pipeline Executions]

    %% Platform Services
    Dashboard -->|queries| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>HTTPS/443]
    Dashboard -->|accesses| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry<br/>HTTPS/443]
    Dashboard -->|reads| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>Service Discovery]
    Dashboard -->|queries| Events[Kubernetes Events<br/>Audit Trail]

